-- Nikkei 225 January Options Settle at 10,771.98, Data Shows
-- B y   Y o s h i a k i   N o h a r a
-- 2013-01-11T00:18:10Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-01-11/nikkei-225-january-options-settle-at-10-771-98-data-shows.html
Japan’s Nikkei 225 January options
settled at 10,771.98, according to data compiled by Bloomberg.  The Nikkei 225 Stock Average gained 1.6 percent to
10,821.34 as of 9:11 a.m. in  Tokyo . The gauge closed at
10,652.64 yesterday.  The settlement price, also known as the “special
quotation,” of Nikkei 225 options is calculated after all
stocks in the Nikkei 225 begin trading.  To contact the reporter for this story:
Yoshiaki Nohara in Tokyo at 
 ynohara1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
